<p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">历史因铭记而永恒，精神因传承而不朽。红色作品展不仅对学生们个人的成长有着积极的影响，也具有重要的社会价值；不仅能增强学生们的家国情怀和历史担当，还能培养出一批爱国主义精神高尚、社会责任感强的社会接班人。青年一代学子将成为推动社会进步和国家发展的重要力量。本次活动接近尾声，感谢为本次展出付出汗水与劳动的老师们、志愿者们。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713430981316080558.png" title="1713430981316080558.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 241); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">本次</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.2px; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">“红色作品展”完美闭幕</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 241); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在实施过程中取得了显著的成果</span></p><p draggable="true" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; color: 